text: Kim Hyo-jin (born 1984) is a South Korean actress. Other notable people with the same name include: * Kim Hyo-jin (footballer) (born 1990), South Korean footballer * Kim Hyo-jin (model) (born 1982), South Korean model * JeA (real name Kim Hyo-jin, born 1981), South Korean singer and member of Brown Eyed Girls * Kim Hyo-jin (born 1994), South Korean singer, member of ONF
title: Kim Hyo-jin (disambiguation)
